title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 15 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 15 2022
description:
Syndicated radio show host Jesse Kelly joins Clay and Buck to bring the heat on every topic from Biden, to Twitter, to whether the '80s were a better decade than the '90s. Clay makes the case for Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade. The Great Migration: Where Americans are moving. C&B holiday edition: The Best Easter Candy.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
